This version of the planner has been modified by Steven Woods 

Changes

1. Oct 24/96  created new domain CAETI
2. Oct 24/96  adapated all three planners (T/A/M) to allow for the
   insistence of use of new operators rather than existing ones for
   a domain-dependent subset of planning operators.  This set is defined
   in the domain definition.
3. Oct 29/96  repaired use of "existing-only" in all three planners to 
   EXCLUDE new operators as establishers when set.

by David Pautler:
4. Nov 13/96  added global var *dp-debug* to toggle debug stmts
   preferred by DP.  This is a disjoint set of format stmts from
   those used by Steve, and :debug-mode is left NIL during their
   use.